    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。您说的LMS门户是指整个系统入口，还是特指教师和学生登录的那个前端界面？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "是入口层，但它同时连接了成绩同步服务和底层的学生数据库。我们可以用子图来区分层次。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，我建议先画两个子图：一个叫Education_StudentDB，包含GradeSync节点和LMS门户节点；另一个叫Education_GradeSync，放具体的业务服务。这样层次更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "subgraph L",
        "subgraph T",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "这个划分合理。第一个子图L代表数据层，第二个子图T代表业务逻辑层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "subgraph L",
        "subgraph T"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已创建两个子图。现在在子图L中，GradeSync节点需要指向自身吗？还是指向另一个GradeSync实例？",
