    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "理解了，我画一个从GradeSync到自身的连接，再画一条到LMS门户的线。接下来子图T里面需要放哪些服务？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
